title: 2Moons: The Ambassador
overview: This sequel continues from where 2 Moons 2 left off. Pha has to persevere in times of helplessness as Wayo's incriminating pictures and videos have been released by Park and Pring. The story will show the progression of their relationship after that scenario. Ming and Kit will have to learn to develop and mature in their relationship, while Forth and Beam will also settle down and progress in theirs.
